Huawei has launched its Nova smartphone in South Africa at a recommended retail price of R6,999. The Nova features a multi-curve design, cameras that promise vivid photography, and solid performance. “South Africans by nature are dynamic consumers. As such, they demand a device that keeps up with their fast-paced lifestyle,” said Zhao Likun, general manager of Huawei South Africa’s consumer business group. The Huawei Nova will be available in South Africa from all mobile operators, it said. Specifications of the device are summarised below.